data.description: Price Improvement!! Enjoying living in this CUSTOM DESIGNED POOL HOME on a large lot with SIDE-ENTRY GARAGE in gorgeous LAKE JOANNA ESTATES with private access to spring fed Lake Joanna. Far from ordinary, this home is the only one of its kind in this boutique style community of 46 homes. Enter into a spacious open floor plan recently remodeled to create a more open look. Upon entering you’ll find a dining room great for holiday meals and in the family area you’ll find a beautiful WOOD BURNING FIREPLACE. Open the sliding doors and find an entertaining oasis in the 10x30 covered FLORIDA ROOM where you can enjoy an amazing view of the large FENCED backyard and OPEN-AIR POOL. Custom kitchen with wood floors is gorgeous and includes solid wood cabinets, granite counter tops, double oven, decorative backsplash, two pantries, and large designer inspired butcher block center island with plenty of room to enjoy your morning breakfast. Kitchen also has a large eat in space with sliding doors out to a tiled patio making this room light and bright. The master suite has a fireplace, walk-in closet, and sliding doors leading out to the Florida Room. En-suite master bath has a garden tub, walk-in shower, granite counter tops and linen closet. This SPLIT FLOOR PLAN has two additional spacious bedrooms with large closets and share a guest bath with granite counter tops tub/shower, and linen closet. roof was replaced in 2019. Just a short distance away is Lake Joanna’s private community boat ramp, gazebo, boat docking and secure boat storage where you can enjoy water-skiing, fishing, canoeing, kayaking or a picnic, along with an area to park your boat for a nominal fee. Your HOA fees include dual water systems; potable water for drinking and lake water for irrigation. Just minutes from downtown Eustis and historical Mt. Dora with shopping and dining and easy access to Hwy. 429, make this your home today!
